Name: JamG
About the game: Control an ever-changing ball along a narrow winding course suspended in midair. Solve your way through challenging levels jam-packed with obstacles, traps and mazes. Morph the marble ball, altering it's size and mass on the spot to more easily get through brain twisting puzzles and platforming challenges.
